ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v23.message

Class OMD_O01

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractStructure
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractGroup
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractMessage
          • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v23.message.OMD_O01
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Group, Message, Structure, Visitable, Serializable

    public class OMD_O01
extends AbstractMessage

    Represents a OMD_O01 message structure (see chapter 4.6). This structure contains the following elements:

    • 1: MSH (Message header segment)
    • 2: NTE (Notes and comments segment) optional repeating
    • 3: OMD_O01_PATIENT (a Group object) optional
    • 4: OMD_O01_ORDER_DIET (a Group object) repeating
    • 5: OMD_O01_ORDER_TRAY (a Group object) optional repeating
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
